Text: "#HARDA\nHere we go!!! India's Heart Harda in Madhya Pradesh a small district\
  \ an my neighborhood, when Mahatma Gandhi had come Harda in 1933 he named (\u0939\
  \u0943\u0926\u092F \u0938\u094D\u0925\u0932\u0940 \u0939\u0930\u0926\u093E) india's\
  \ heart.\nThere is a campanile which is center of Harda and around  this campanile\
  \ whole market is \nsituated, hrada's market is very popular where can get good\
  \ clothes it can branded or with no brands, you can do complete shoping with limited\
  \ budget, even you can shop for your wedding all traditional style lehengas and\
  \ sherwani, you will get all kind of Masalas and street foods and different types\
  \ of fabrics, Here a fort in Makrai call Makrai fort and it was prince residance\
  \ in the time of British Administration, It gives 15- 20 percent support to India\
  \ in wheat production, holly river Narmada's Umbilicus is there, there are many\
  \ temple to visit with there different recital such as khet wali mata temple, gupteshvar\
  \ mandir, Saibaba Temple etc, Another well-known mela, the month-long Bhilat Dev\
  \ is organised every year.\npeople use here Nimadi, Malwi for day to day communication.\
  \ Many people don't know about this because it's a small district but the city contains\
  \ it's own history"
